Package: docker-cleanup
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: docker-ce | docker.io, whiptail
Maintainer: Dedan Okware <softengdedan@gmail.com>
Description: Interactive Docker cleanup utility
 This package provides an interactive cleanup utility for Docker containers
 and resources. It allows users to configure cleanup schedules and select
 which containers to clean up. Features include:
  - Interactive terminal interface with colorful UI
  - Configurable cleanup schedules
  - Selective container cleanup
  - Automated periodic cleanup
  - Detailed logging and status reporting

